{"tid":1762721,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"同情艾馬利　摩連奴：佢好快有新工","createTime":"2019-11-29T19:02:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-01T11:25:53.000Z","uid":16659,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"1fd3869285e3274bf7390a83f3afd106021479fa","tid":1762721,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T19:02:34.000Z","msg":"於歐霸盃主場1:2反敗予法蘭克福後，阿仙奴終於怒炒領隊艾馬利，由龍格保上任成看守領隊。對於艾帥被炒，熱刺新主帥摩連奴表示同情，但他肯定艾帥的實力，認為好快就有其他大球會聘他為帥。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴本季處多事之秋，無論於英超或盃賽的表現都不理想，目前僅列聯賽榜中游，而於歐霸盃表現亦無說服力。另外又發生格列沙加挑釁球迷事件，艾馬利終於丟掉帥印。剛接手熱刺帥印的摩連奴表示：「這是個悲傷的消息。我曾看過父親被炒，自己亦曾失去工作，所以每次看到其他領隊被辭退也不好受，因為我感同身受。」<br />\n<br />\n「雖然是傷感，但這就是現實。艾馬利是位頂級領隊，於阿仙奴發展得不如意，但他肯定是個好領隊，之前的成績已說明了一切。艾帥現應好好休息一下，之後就會有另一間大球會叩他的門，之後他的職業生涯就能撥亂反正。艾馬利，加油！」(<a href=\"http://goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fgoal.com&d=upH1NnktvNch8HeVEtNbY0YZmLIq74JPLN0FyuDKESI%3D&h=ad903eb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"65d61c0ca65a18eb332f392aa2422c8ab0332613","tid":1762721,"uid":124891,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T19:13:51.000Z","msg":"被炒師圍爐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77b0d8e7c92242f97ced4bfe95d7dd0b7848c6a9","tid":1762721,"uid":149607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T20:10:07.000Z","msg":"好能搶口<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"668d34dd049c66b36ecad5437820d53d8af11c11","tid":1762721,"uid":165817,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-29T21:24:03.000Z","msg":"又撥亂反正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e815ef724c1e6414ce5b6b3332dd35798b7a9039","tid":1762721,"uid":249657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T01:27:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />daddy 最近變到好識講野"},{"pid":"0370f0f12defaa4787639dab1f919dbac7b13032","tid":1762721,"uid":158006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T01:37:02.000Z","msg":"Daddy啲中文幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2734b380700c2f4e26bd9ea04090d6f700978bc0","tid":1762721,"uid":273774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:03:44.000Z","msg":"撥亂反正英文點講"},{"pid":"36b3e1177b9a85582746df20744c16ac7bf503b1","tid":1762721,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2734b380700c2f4e26bd9ea04090d6f700978bc0","tid":1762721,"uid":273774,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-30T04:03:44.000Z","msg":"撥亂反正英文點講"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-01T11:25:53.000Z","msg":"erect randomly upside down"}]}